description: A few stray branches hang over the balcony, giving it a secluded, wooded feel.  The treetops of the Upper Trollfang stretch before you, branches rustling in a soft breeze.  Birds sing in the fresh air, insects buzz, and a stray hill troll glances upwards, shaking his fist angrily.

title: [Abandoned Inn, Balcony]
